(16927, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_4_content', 'Their network and know-how were great assets to our efforts. Their staff diligently executed and moved fast to capitalize on emerging opportunities.\r\n'),
(16928, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_4_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
