(478, 1, '2017-04-17 18:52:06', '2017-04-17 18:52:06', 'In The Love Dare Day by Day, 52 biblically based daresone a weekchallenge readers to more deeply live out unconditional love in their marriages. Behind each dare, a daily devotion amplifies the scriptural principle. More than 100 Go Deeper selections give even more biblical insight. The Love Dare Day by Day also offers a free online marriage-evaluation resource, keyed to select material in the book.\r\n\r\nBrothers, pastors, filmmakers and authors, Alex and Stephen Kendrick co-wrote the international bestsellers The Love Dare, The Love Dare for Parents and The Resolution for Men. They are among the co-founders of Sherwood Pictures and worked together to write and produce the hit Christian films FLYWHEEL, FACING THE GIANTS, FIREPROOF and COURAGEOUS. Kendrick Brothers Productions is expanding their movie productions with renewed focus on encouraging and equipping the next generation of Christian filmmakers (kendrickbrothers.com). Alex and Stephen continue to serve on the pastoral staff of Sherwood Baptist Church in Albany, Ga.', 'The Love Dare Day By Day: A Year Of Devotions For Couples', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-love-dare-day-by-day-a-year-of-devotions-for-couples', '', '', '2017-07-14 18:37:27', '2017-07-14 18:37:27', '', 0, 'http://lovell-fairchild.dev//?post_type=clients&#038;p=478', 31, 'clients', '', 0),
