(672, 1, '2017-04-21 19:07:49', '2017-04-21 19:07:49', 'Before she succumbs to cancer, the dying wish of Laura Mayfield-Bennett is to be reunited with the daughter she never knew. Unfortunately, that daughter, Katie Lapp, is a member of the Amish order. Katie is about to be married, but uneasy about the path ahead. Now she discovers the secret her parents have kept from her: she\'s adopted.\n\nThe film is based on the celebrated first novel of the best-selling "The Heritage of Lancaster County" book series from author Beverly Lewis. Stars Danielle Panabaker &amp; Sherry Stringfield.', 'The Shunning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '372-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-04-21 19:07:49', '2017-04-21 19:07:49', '', 372, 'http://lovell-fairchild.dev//2017/04/21/372-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
