(1089, 1, '2017-07-12 22:30:08', '2017-07-12 22:30:08', '<strong><em>Get LowReflections on Pride and Humility</em></strong>is hard to explain. Meticulously researched, highly readable, its essays explore humility in illustrations, anecdotes, asides and footnoted references (also readable) from Bob Dylan to George Jones, Plato, John Paul II, and John Stott. Oh, and the Bible. In<strong><em>Get Low,</em></strong>attorney, erstwhile cop, seminary graduate, graduate professor and Young Life leader Jack Wisdom<strong><em></em></strong>looks at prides many forms and effects in culture, society and in individual lives; then he turns to what God says about humility.', 'Get Low', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'get-low-the-book__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-14 17:54:05', '2017-07-14 17:54:05', '', 0, 'http://lovell-fairchild.dev/?post_type=clients&#038;p=1089', 166, 'clients', '', 0),
